# ============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.docker.template .env
# 2. Fill in your Azure OpenAI credentials
# 3. Fill in your Canvas LMS credentials
# 4. Save the file
# 5. Run: docker-compose up --build
# 6. Access the app at http://localhost:8080
# ============================================================================
